      <h1>Coffee & Cars car show, something to do on a Saturday</h1>
      <p><strong>By <a href="../authors/calebhuffman.html">Caleb Huffman</a></strong></p>
      <p><em>March 18, 2025</em></p>

      <p>
        HOUSTON – The first Saturday of each month there is a car show held at POST Houston,<p> 
      <p> by Coffee & Cars, a group of car enthusiasts who look to make an enjoyable event for people<p>
      <p> of all ages. You can find many types of vehicles here, from Ferraris to classic American muscle cars.
        <!-- trimmed for brevity -->
        Go check it out and tell us what you think in the comments below.
      </p>

